text: Alessandra Carina Mastronardi (born February 18, 1986) is an Italian actress. She is best known for her roles in the movies To Rome with Love and The Unbearable Weight of Massive Talent. She also played Francesca in the television series Master of None. ==References== ==Other websites== * Category:1986 births Category:Living people Category:Italian movie actors Category:Italian television actors Category:Italian voice actors Category:Italian stage actors Category:Actors from Naples
